ZH: 水的底很深。
EN: The bottom of the water is very deep.

ZH: 他坐在椅子的底上。
EN: He sat on the bottom of the chair.

ZH: 他们把书本放在桌子的底下。
EN: They put the books under the table.

ZH: 这个杯子的底是圆的。
EN: The bottom of this cup is round.

ZH: 我们发现了一个宝藏，藏在山的底下。
EN: We found a treasure hidden at the bottom of the mountain.

ZH: 香蕉的底部有一块黑色的斑点。
EN: There is a black spot at the bottom of the banana.

ZH: 这个箱子的底部很结实。
EN: The bottom of this box is very sturdy.

ZH: 他们在房间的底部装了地暖。
EN: They installed underfloor heating at the bottom of the room.

ZH: 他用橡皮擦掉了纸的底部字迹。
EN: He erased the writing at the bottom of the paper with an eraser.

ZH: 河底的泥土很松软。
EN: The mud at the bottom of the river is soft.

ZH: 这个玻璃杯的底部很厚。
EN: The bottom of this glass is very thick.

ZH: 我找到了我的钥匙，它掉在床底下了。
EN: I found my keys, they fell under the bed.

ZH: 天空船从尘土飞扬的废墟中穿过。
EN: The skyship flew through the swirling dust and debris.

ZH: 妈妈把袋子放在冰箱底下了。
EN: Mom put the bag under the fridge.

ZH: 开车的时候要注意路底不平。
EN: Watch out for uneven road surfaces when driving.

ZH: 鸟儿在草丛中寻找庇护的地方。
EN: The birds seek shelter in the bottom of the bushes.

ZH: 隐藏在橱柜底下的老鼠惊了一跳。
EN: The mouse hidden at the bottom of the cupboard was startled.

ZH: 我们找到了这个城市的底层社会。
EN: We uncovered the underbelly of this city's society.

ZH: 孩子们在海底发现了一种奇特的珍珠。
EN: The children discovered a strange pearl on the ocean floor.

ZH: 纸箱的底部有一个小孔。
EN: There is a small hole at the bottom of the cardboard box.
